snippet.title: Vortex (SNES) First Stage
snippet.description: This is the first level of the game Vortex for the Super Nintendo. This game is very difficult but the good thing is it has a password system. Most likely you'll lose a bunch of times before you figure out how to defeat most of the bosses from each stage. Man I love the music.
